pe of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSEMBLY_SKILL_GROUP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SKILL_SUBTITLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assembly Hero Skill</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umiejętność bohatera Zgromadzenia</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill tree header.
Assembly is an-game race.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BATTLEFIELD_REPAIRS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Battlefield Repairs</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Naprawy bojowe</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BATTLEFIELD_REPAIRS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Being an expert in repairs, the hero heals each Cyborg and Mechanical unit in the army for {BattlefieldHeal}  after each battle.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ten bohater to specjalista od napraw, który po każdej bitwie przywraca cyborgom i jednostkom mechanicznym w armii {BattlefieldHeal}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Cyborg and Mechanical are in-game unit types. 
Commander in this context means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BATTLEFIELD_REPAIRS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Heals for {BattlefieldHeal} after each battle.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Przywraca {BattlefieldHeal} po każdej bitwie.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CYBERNETIC_OVERDRIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cybernetic Overdrive</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cybernetyczne przeciążenie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CYBERNETIC_OVERDRIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Target friendly Cyborg or Mechanical unit has all their action points refilled. [br/]Doesn't work on units that are unable to move and take actions.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Przywraca wszystkie punkty akcji wybranej przyjaznej jednostce mechanicznej lub cyborgowi.[br/]Nie działa na jednostki, które nie mogą się poruszać ani działać.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Action points are in-game points spent on actions.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NANITE_BOOSTERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nanite Boosters</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nanitowe wzmocnienie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NANITE_BOOSTERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Advanced nanite boosters provide all units in the army with +{NaniteResistance} resistance to all status effects.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zaawansowane nanitowe wzmocnienie zapewnia wszystkim jednostkom w armii +{NaniteResistance} do odporności na wszystkie efekty stanu.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Commander in this context means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NANITE_BOOSTERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero's nanite boosters give this unit +{NaniteResistance} resistance to all status effects.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nanitowe wzmocnienie bohatera zapewnia tej jednostce +{NaniteResistance} do odporności na wszystkie efekty stanu.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STUNNING_DISCHARGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Stunning Discharge</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Oszałamiające wyładowanie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STUNNING_DISCHARGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero has a built in discharge module. When activated, it deals damage to all adjacent friendly and enemy units. </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater ma wbudowany moduł wyładowań. Po aktywacji zadaje on obrażenia wszystkim sąsiednim przyjaznym i wrogim jednostkom. </Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STABILIZERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Stabilizers</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Stabilizatory</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STABILIZERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Advanced stabilizers grant the hero one level of [abilityblue]Stagger Resistance.[/abilityblue]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zaawansowane stabilizatory zapewniają bohaterowi jeden poziom [abilityblue]odporności na zachwianie[/abilityblue].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Stagger resistance is in-game unit stat.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Text between {} should NOT be localized as they are numerical values in-game. Text between [] should NOT be localized as they are either icons or text formatting

